# Atmos Stack Conventions

- Org defaults go in `stacks/orgs/homelab/_defaults.yaml` (namespace, tags, backend config)
- Component defaults go in `stacks/catalog/{terraform,ansible,helmfile}/{name}.yaml`
- Environment stacks go in `stacks/deploy/{stage}/{stack}.yaml`
- Environment stacks MUST import `orgs/homelab/_defaults` plus relevant catalog entries
- Override only environment-specific values under `components.{type}.{name}.vars`
- Naming uses Cloud Posse label: `{namespace}-{environment}-{stage}-{name}`
- Backend key template: `terraform/{{ .component }}/{{ .vars.stage }}.tfstate`
- When adding a new component: create catalog, import in deploy stacks, add to workflows
